name: Cat & Mouse
description:
On a huge farm in Arb-Metaverse, the farmer filled the barn with rice, which was a bumper year.
But what he needs to be vigilant about is that a crowd of mice are staring at his barn. Fortunately, the farmer noticed them, a crowd of cats, yes a crowd of cats can solve this problem.The farmer's barn has a guardian - a crowd of loyal cats?

But,things don't seem that simple...
